s_window\",\n    \"challenges.bonus_completions_window\",\n  ];\n\nexport type PeekChallengesOverview = {\n  generatedAt: string;\n  metrics: ReadonlyArray<PeekMetric>;\n};\n","numLines":141,"startLine":1054,"totalLines":1194}}}
